{"componentChunkName":"component---node-modules-gatsby-theme-portfolio-minimal-src-templates-article-index-tsx","path":"/my-first-article/howgatsby2/","result":{"pageContext":{"article":{"banner":{"alt":"[Gatsby / Github Blog] gatsby-theme-portfolio-minimal 폴더 상세 정리해보기 (2)","caption":"Photo by <u><a href=\"https://unsplash.com/photos/Nc5Q_CEcY44\">Gatsby</a></u>","src":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/403ef70575444215ce3304a8a17629ba/bc51f/Gatsby.png","srcSet":"/static/403ef70575444215ce3304a8a17629ba/41200/Gatsby.png 165w,\n/static/403ef70575444215ce3304a8a17629ba/f979a/Gatsby.png 330w,\n/static/403ef70575444215ce3304a8a17629ba/bc51f/Gatsby.png 660w","sizes":"(min-width: 660px) 660px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/403ef70575444215ce3304a8a17629ba/322ad/Gatsby.webp 165w,\n/static/403ef70575444215ce3304a8a17629ba/de3b3/Gatsby.webp 330w,\n/static/403ef70575444215ce3304a8a17629ba/2b2b5/Gatsby.webp 660w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 660px) 660px, 100vw"}]},"width":660,"height":400}}}},"body":"<h2>🥳 Gatsby로 Github Blog 개시 완료하다!!</h2>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 74.54545454545453%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/3f32fe6da91d188b6a169a98f5b796a2/c9b55/nowblog_img.webp 165w,\n/static/3f32fe6da91d188b6a169a98f5b796a2/f2908/nowblog_img.webp 330w,\n/static/3f32fe6da91d188b6a169a98f5b796a2/cc661/nowblog_img.webp 660w,\n/static/3f32fe6da91d188b6a169a98f5b796a2/a66df/nowblog_img.webp 990w,\n/static/3f32fe6da91d188b6a169a98f5b796a2/3718f/nowblog_img.webp 1201w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/3f32fe6da91d188b6a169a98f5b796a2/04c57/nowblog_img.png 165w,\n/static/3f32fe6da91d188b6a169a98f5b796a2/d9ecf/nowblog_img.png 330w,\n/static/3f32fe6da91d188b6a169a98f5b796a2/1f083/nowblog_img.png 660w,\n/static/3f32fe6da91d188b6a169a98f5b796a2/7a3d6/nowblog_img.png 990w,\n/static/3f32fe6da91d188b6a169a98f5b796a2/690c6/nowblog_img.png 1201w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/3f32fe6da91d188b6a169a98f5b796a2/1f083/nowblog_img.png\"\n            alt=\"This is the alt tag.\"\n            title=\"Now My Github Blog that use Gatsby\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p>Now My Github Blog that use Gatsby</p></figcaption>\n  </figure>\n완전히 이전을 완료하였고, 현재 바뀐 내 블로그 모습이다. 이제는 내껄로 모든걸 수정을 해야한다. 기존에 위치에서 내가 쓸 것들만 남기고, 필요한건 추가 해야한다. <em><strong>gatsby-theme-portfolio-minimal</strong></em> 이 테마 자체가 아직 많이 사용하는 것 같지가 않다. 그래서 혹시라도 사용하실 분이 있다는 가정하에 그리고 내가 기록을 남기기 위해 블로그 글로 작성하기로 했다.</p>\n<h2>🤔 우리가 집중해서 봐야하는 폴더, 파일들</h2>\n<p>우리가 주요하게 사용하게될 폴더는 content폴더이다. 그중에서 우선 sections 폴더를 먼저 보겠다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">content\n    └── sections\n    │ └── about\n    │     └── about.md # has to be Markdown\n    │ └── contact\n    │     └── contact.json # has to be JSON\n    │ └── hero\n    │     └── hero.json # has to be JSON\n    │ └── interests\n    │     └── interests.json # has to be JSON\n    │ └── legal\n    │     └── imprint.md # has to be Markdown\n    │ └── projects\n    │     └── projects.json # has to be JSON</code></pre></div>\n<p>여기서 거의 메인 홈페이지의 글들을 처리한다고 봐도 무방하다. about폴더부터 어디를 다루는지 살펴보겠다.</p>\n<h3>about/about.md</h3>\n<p>about 폴더 안에는 about.md로 마크다운 파일이 들어있다. 코드를 보게되면 다음과 같다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">---\nimageSrc: \"../../images/charles-deluvio-DgoyKNgPiFQ-unsplash.jpg\"\nimageAlt: \"About Gatsby Theme Portfolio Minimal\"\n---\n\nPortfolio Minimal is a Gatsby Theme that creates outstanding one-pages portfolio within minutes!\n\nIt has predefined sections for your bio, skills, projects, and contact details. If you are a writer on Medium, you can integrate your latest articles in a distinct section as well. While building the theme, I tried to keep the setup as simple as possible while keeping everything configurable if you like to.\n\nUsing theme composition, you can easily customize the CSS theme to your own preferences - e.g. change colors, fonts, etc.\n\nLast but not least, it has some cool features you can opt-in to: Dark Mode, Splash Screen, Cookie Banner, and more to find out :)\n\nPhoto by &lt;a href=\"https://unsplash.com/@charlesdeluvio?utm_source=unsplash&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_content=creditCopyText\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" aria-label=\"External Link\">&lt;u>Charles Deluvio&lt;/u>&lt;/a> on Unsplash</code></pre></div>\n<p>그리고 다음 사진은 이 md파일이 적용되는 위치이다.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 55.757575757575765%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/6c205af279a8531f3cb5fc104a7cdde2/c9b55/about_md.webp 165w,\n/static/6c205af279a8531f3cb5fc104a7cdde2/f2908/about_md.webp 330w,\n/static/6c205af279a8531f3cb5fc104a7cdde2/cc661/about_md.webp 660w,\n/static/6c205af279a8531f3cb5fc104a7cdde2/a66df/about_md.webp 990w,\n/static/6c205af279a8531f3cb5fc104a7cdde2/37c82/about_md.webp 1089w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/6c205af279a8531f3cb5fc104a7cdde2/04c57/about_md.png 165w,\n/static/6c205af279a8531f3cb5fc104a7cdde2/d9ecf/about_md.png 330w,\n/static/6c205af279a8531f3cb5fc104a7cdde2/1f083/about_md.png 660w,\n/static/6c205af279a8531f3cb5fc104a7cdde2/7a3d6/about_md.png 990w,\n/static/6c205af279a8531f3cb5fc104a7cdde2/96e86/about_md.png 1089w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/6c205af279a8531f3cb5fc104a7cdde2/1f083/about_md.png\"\n            alt=\"스크린샷\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n<em><strong>imageAlt</strong></em> 부분이 글의 최상단 제목같은 부분이 되는거 같고 <em><strong>imageSrc</strong></em> 이부분이 이미지가 적용되는 부분인거 같다.</p>\n<h3>contact/contact.json</h3>\n<p>다음 살펴볼 파일은 contact폴더 안에 contact.json 폴더 이다. 적용되는 위치랑 코드를 살펴보며서 설명하겠다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">{\n  \"name\": \"DataEngineer Ji Min Chur\",\n  \"email\": \"ttlcc1364@gmail.com\",\n  \"description\": \"If you have any problems with this Blog, create an issue in the GitHub repository.\",\n  \"image\": {\n    \"src\": \"../../images/main_img2.jpeg\",\n    \"alt\": \"Minchur's Logo\"\n  },\n  \"socialProfiles\": {\n    \"from\": [\"LinkedIn\", \"Github\", \"Mail\"],\n    \"showIcons\": true\n  }\n}</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 57.57575757575757%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/d03eb8b62a2be0ccc3ff86a8b63f190f/c9b55/contact_json.webp 165w,\n/static/d03eb8b62a2be0ccc3ff86a8b63f190f/f2908/contact_json.webp 330w,\n/static/d03eb8b62a2be0ccc3ff86a8b63f190f/cc661/contact_json.webp 660w,\n/static/d03eb8b62a2be0ccc3ff86a8b63f190f/42cfc/contact_json.webp 781w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/d03eb8b62a2be0ccc3ff86a8b63f190f/04c57/contact_json.png 165w,\n/static/d03eb8b62a2be0ccc3ff86a8b63f190f/d9ecf/contact_json.png 330w,\n/static/d03eb8b62a2be0ccc3ff86a8b63f190f/1f083/contact_json.png 660w,\n/static/d03eb8b62a2be0ccc3ff86a8b63f190f/7fee5/contact_json.png 781w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/d03eb8b62a2be0ccc3ff86a8b63f190f/1f083/contact_json.png\"\n            alt=\"스크린샷\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n눈으로 만 봐도 어디에 어떤부분이 적용되는 지 바로 알수가 있다! 밑에 socialProfiles부분의 링크는 다른 파일에서 설정을 할 수가 있으니 우선 여기서는 필요한 것들만 남기고 넘어 가도록 하겠다.</p>\n<h3>hero/hero.json</h3>\n<p>이제 Github Blog의 얼굴이 될수 있는 제일 먼저 보이는 부분이다. 우선 코드랑 사진부터 살펴 보겠다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">{\n  \"intro\": \"Hej\",\n  \"heroPhoto\": {\n    \"src\": \"../../images/lego-dummy.png\",\n    \"alt\": \"My Photo\"\n  },\n  \"image\": {\n    \"src\": \"../../images/waving-hand.png\",\n    \"alt\": \"Waving Hand Emoji\"\n  },\n  \"title\": \"I'm a Gatsby Starter\",\n  \"subtitle\": {\n    \"prefix\": \"I do all the setup \",\n    \"highlight\": \"for you\",\n    \"suffix\": \".\"\n  },\n  \"description\": \"A Gatsby Starter Project to easily get started with Portfolio Minimal theme.\",\n  \"socialProfiles\": {\n    \"from\": [\"LinkedIn\", \"Medium\", \"Github\", \"Mail\"],\n    \"showIcons\": false\n  }\n}</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 48.484848484848484%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/5b83f67f29dd7d98695cfc5e5835444f/c9b55/hero_json.webp 165w,\n/static/5b83f67f29dd7d98695cfc5e5835444f/f2908/hero_json.webp 330w,\n/static/5b83f67f29dd7d98695cfc5e5835444f/cc661/hero_json.webp 660w,\n/static/5b83f67f29dd7d98695cfc5e5835444f/a66df/hero_json.webp 990w,\n/static/5b83f67f29dd7d98695cfc5e5835444f/aa5f8/hero_json.webp 1007w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/5b83f67f29dd7d98695cfc5e5835444f/04c57/hero_json.png 165w,\n/static/5b83f67f29dd7d98695cfc5e5835444f/d9ecf/hero_json.png 330w,\n/static/5b83f67f29dd7d98695cfc5e5835444f/1f083/hero_json.png 660w,\n/static/5b83f67f29dd7d98695cfc5e5835444f/7a3d6/hero_json.png 990w,\n/static/5b83f67f29dd7d98695cfc5e5835444f/54bf4/hero_json.png 1007w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/5b83f67f29dd7d98695cfc5e5835444f/1f083/hero_json.png\"\n            alt=\"스크린샷\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n<em><strong>intro</strong></em>부분은 제일 크게 쓰여지는 글이라고 보여진다. 기본테마를 가져와서 보면 메인 페이지 부분에는 이미지가 따로 존재하지 않는다. 그래서 <em><strong>heroPhoto</strong></em>부분이 설정이 되어 있어도 보이지가 않는 이유가 이것이다. 원하는 이미지로 설정하고 넣으면 오른쪽부분에 뜰 것이다.</p>\n<p>나머지 부분들은 보면 알 수 있었지만 내가 보았을때 잠깐 헷갈렸던 부분은 <em><strong>subtitle</strong></em>부분이다. 나는 prefix에 글을 쓰고 highligt을 주고 또 글을 쓰고 싶었었다.. 그래서 자세히 살펴보니깐 suffix에 .으로 되어있었다 그렇다.. prefix,suffix에는 그냥글을 쓰면 되고 중간에 하이라이트를 주고 싶으면 highlight부분에다가 쓰면 된다.</p>\n<h3>interests/interests.json</h3>\n<p>다음으로 살펴볼 파일은 interests.json파일이다. 우선 코드랑 사진을 살펴보자</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">{\n  \"interests\": [\n    {\n      \"label\": \"Quick and Easy Setup\",\n      \"image\": {\n        \"src\": \"../../images/joystick.png\",\n        \"alt\": \"\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"label\": \"Content via Markdown\",\n      \"image\": {\n        \"src\": \"../../images/notebook.png\",\n        \"alt\": \"\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"label\": \"Responsive Design\",\n      \"image\": {\n        \"src\": \"../../images/nail-polish.png\",\n        \"alt\": \"\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"label\": \"Medium Integration\",\n      \"image\": {\n        \"src\": \"../../images/medium.png\",\n        \"alt\": \"\"\n      }\n    },\n    ...\n     ],\n  \"button\": {\n    \"visible\": true,\n    \"label\": \"+ Load More\",\n    \"initiallyShownInterests\": 5\n  }\n}</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 31.51515151515152%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/8b26f340df2691b481645d7323cef66b/c9b55/interests_json.webp 165w,\n/static/8b26f340df2691b481645d7323cef66b/f2908/interests_json.webp 330w,\n/static/8b26f340df2691b481645d7323cef66b/cc661/interests_json.webp 660w,\n/static/8b26f340df2691b481645d7323cef66b/85db8/interests_json.webp 961w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/8b26f340df2691b481645d7323cef66b/04c57/interests_json.png 165w,\n/static/8b26f340df2691b481645d7323cef66b/d9ecf/interests_json.png 330w,\n/static/8b26f340df2691b481645d7323cef66b/1f083/interests_json.png 660w,\n/static/8b26f340df2691b481645d7323cef66b/024d6/interests_json.png 961w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/8b26f340df2691b481645d7323cef66b/1f083/interests_json.png\"\n            alt=\"스크린샷\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n이것도 읽어보면서 사진을 보면 대충 감이 온다. 원래 테마는 자신의 취미/흥미를 적어 놨지만 나는 여기를 사용할수있는 기술스택들로 바꿔놓을 생각이다.</p>\n<h3>legal/*.md</h3>\n<p>legal폴더 안에는 2개의 markdown폴더가 존재 한다. 처음에는 어디에 적용이 되는 건지 한참 찾아봤었다 포스팅 글도 아니고 그렇다고 메인페이지에 적용이 되어있는거 같진 않았었다. 그러다가 우연히 footer쪽을 보게 되었는데 오른쪽에 떡하니 있었다...\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 16.363636363636363%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAADCAYAAACTWi8uAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAAXUlEQVR42o2MiwkAIQxD/SCiaBfQ/ccSq4PkLp3AwoMmJHH3XpxzsNaCqoL6FebZJXtv81wIAbVWzDnRe4f3HjHGJ5jPOaOUAhEBt9x/Zo4xLED9SmsNKSXr86f/Af2Xc0jdOdb6AAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/7da989679c8550ee38fc2c7039753e89/c9b55/leagl(1).webp 165w,\n/static/7da989679c8550ee38fc2c7039753e89/f2908/leagl(1).webp 330w,\n/static/7da989679c8550ee38fc2c7039753e89/cc661/leagl(1).webp 660w,\n/static/7da989679c8550ee38fc2c7039753e89/a66df/leagl(1).webp 990w,\n/static/7da989679c8550ee38fc2c7039753e89/09917/leagl(1).webp 1079w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/7da989679c8550ee38fc2c7039753e89/04c57/leagl(1).png 165w,\n/static/7da989679c8550ee38fc2c7039753e89/d9ecf/leagl(1).png 330w,\n/static/7da989679c8550ee38fc2c7039753e89/1f083/leagl(1).png 660w,\n/static/7da989679c8550ee38fc2c7039753e89/7a3d6/leagl(1).png 990w,\n/static/7da989679c8550ee38fc2c7039753e89/cf4cc/leagl(1).png 1079w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/7da989679c8550ee38fc2c7039753e89/1f083/leagl(1).png\"\n            alt=\"스크린샷\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span></p>\n<p>누르면 밑에 사진들처럼 이동을 하게 된다.\n<figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 78.18181818181817%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/6757942e9b4deddb9a667178995ba2ac/c9b55/leagl(2).webp 165w,\n/static/6757942e9b4deddb9a667178995ba2ac/f2908/leagl(2).webp 330w,\n/static/6757942e9b4deddb9a667178995ba2ac/cc661/leagl(2).webp 660w,\n/static/6757942e9b4deddb9a667178995ba2ac/a66df/leagl(2).webp 990w,\n/static/6757942e9b4deddb9a667178995ba2ac/0b716/leagl(2).webp 1296w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/6757942e9b4deddb9a667178995ba2ac/04c57/leagl(2).png 165w,\n/static/6757942e9b4deddb9a667178995ba2ac/d9ecf/leagl(2).png 330w,\n/static/6757942e9b4deddb9a667178995ba2ac/1f083/leagl(2).png 660w,\n/static/6757942e9b4deddb9a667178995ba2ac/7a3d6/leagl(2).png 990w,\n/static/6757942e9b4deddb9a667178995ba2ac/86a1e/leagl(2).png 1296w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/6757942e9b4deddb9a667178995ba2ac/1f083/leagl(2).png\"\n            alt=\"스크린샷\"\n            title=\"Imprint page\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p>Imprint page</p></figcaption>\n  </figure>\n<figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 67.27272727272727%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/c4d0fdf766e40ead3cda04fab843b838/c9b55/leagl(3).webp 165w,\n/static/c4d0fdf766e40ead3cda04fab843b838/f2908/leagl(3).webp 330w,\n/static/c4d0fdf766e40ead3cda04fab843b838/cc661/leagl(3).webp 660w,\n/static/c4d0fdf766e40ead3cda04fab843b838/a66df/leagl(3).webp 990w,\n/static/c4d0fdf766e40ead3cda04fab843b838/a8acc/leagl(3).webp 1295w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/c4d0fdf766e40ead3cda04fab843b838/04c57/leagl(3).png 165w,\n/static/c4d0fdf766e40ead3cda04fab843b838/d9ecf/leagl(3).png 330w,\n/static/c4d0fdf766e40ead3cda04fab843b838/1f083/leagl(3).png 660w,\n/static/c4d0fdf766e40ead3cda04fab843b838/7a3d6/leagl(3).png 990w,\n/static/c4d0fdf766e40ead3cda04fab843b838/610c0/leagl(3).png 1295w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/c4d0fdf766e40ead3cda04fab843b838/1f083/leagl(3).png\"\n            alt=\"스크린샷\"\n            title=\"Imprint page\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p>Imprint page</p></figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>내가 사용할때 어떤부분을 여기다 넣어야 할지는 아직 생각이 나질않아 우선 그대로 놓은채로 진행중이다.</p>\n<h3>projects/projects.json</h3>\n<p>이 부분은 내가 이 blog중에서 제일 좋아하는 부분이다. 제일 깔끔하고 이쁘게 정리할 수 있게 있는거 같다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">{\n  \"projects\": [\n    {\n      \"visible\": true,\n      \"category\": \"🕹️ EASY AND QUICK SETUP\",\n      \"title\": \"Add content and deploy!\",\n      \"description\": \"Get up and running within minutes. Just install the starter, add your content, deploy it, and there you go! This starter works seamlessly with hosts like Netlify. Photo by Clément H on Unsplash.\",\n      \"tags\": [\"Content Integration\", \"Ready-2-Deploy\"],\n      \"image\": {\n        \"src\": \"../../images/clement-h-95YRwf6CNw8-unsplash.jpg\",\n        \"alt\": \"Quick Setup\",\n        \"linkTo\": \"https://github.com/konstantinmuenster/gatsby-starter-portfolio-minimal-theme\"\n      },\n      \"links\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"github\",\n          \"url\": \"https://github.com/konstantinmuenster/gatsby-starter-portfolio-minimal-theme\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"external\",\n          \"url\": \"https://www.gatsbyjs.org/docs/mdx/writing-pages/\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"visible\": true,\n      \"category\": \"🧰 EXTENDABLE LAYOUT\",\n      \"title\": \"Add more sections!\",\n      \"description\": \"The starter includes predefined sections as well as a template for new, custom sections. Moreover, you can add new projects to this section without additional coding. Photo by Kelly Sikkema on Unsplash.\",\n      \"tags\": [\"Custom Sections\", \"Easy-2-Use\"],\n      \"image\": {\n        \"src\": \"../../images/kelly-sikkema-Hl3LUdyKRic-unsplash.jpg\",\n        \"alt\": \"Extendable Layout\"\n      },\n      \"links\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"github\",\n          \"url\": \"https://github.com/konstantinmuenster/gatsby-starter-portfolio-minimal-theme\"\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n  ],\n  \"button\": {\n    \"visible\": true,\n    \"label\": \"Visit on Github\",\n    \"url\": \"https://github.com/konstantinmuenster/gatsby-theme-portfolio-minimal\"\n  }\n}</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 79.39393939393939%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/ae8b3bea904c670dd76ee8112233e301/c9b55/projects_json.webp 165w,\n/static/ae8b3bea904c670dd76ee8112233e301/f2908/projects_json.webp 330w,\n/static/ae8b3bea904c670dd76ee8112233e301/cc661/projects_json.webp 660w,\n/static/ae8b3bea904c670dd76ee8112233e301/a66df/projects_json.webp 990w,\n/static/ae8b3bea904c670dd76ee8112233e301/42749/projects_json.webp 1051w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/ae8b3bea904c670dd76ee8112233e301/04c57/projects_json.png 165w,\n/static/ae8b3bea904c670dd76ee8112233e301/d9ecf/projects_json.png 330w,\n/static/ae8b3bea904c670dd76ee8112233e301/1f083/projects_json.png 660w,\n/static/ae8b3bea904c670dd76ee8112233e301/7a3d6/projects_json.png 990w,\n/static/ae8b3bea904c670dd76ee8112233e301/58fee/projects_json.png 1051w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/ae8b3bea904c670dd76ee8112233e301/1f083/projects_json.png\"\n            alt=\"스크린샷\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n밑에 사진과 코드들을 번갈아 가면서 보게 되면 어디에 어떤게 적용되는지 알 수 있다.</p>\n<h2>😗 우선 Section 폴더만!!</h2>\n<p>section폴더만 어느정도 파악하면 메인페이지는 어느정도 꾸밀수가 있을것이다. 꾸미고 나니깐 뿌듯하면서 원하던 테마로 blog을 적용시켜 나가니까 jekyll때보다 애정이 2배 더 상승한거 같다.</p>\n<p>다음 [Github Blog] 포스팅때는 Content폴더안에 나머지 파일들에 대해서 글을 써보도록 하겠다.</p>","categories":["Github Blog","Gatsby"],"date":"July 07, 2024","description":"[Gatsby / Github Blog] gatsby-theme-portfolio-minimal 폴더 상세 정리해보기 (2)","id":"efa367e7-4251-5a1e-a3f1-8449f511c261","keywords":["Gitub Blog","Gatsby","jekyll","상세 내용","gatsby-theme-portfolio-minimal"],"slug":"/my-first-article/howgatsby2/","title":"[Gatsby / Github Blog] gatsby-theme-portfolio-minimal 폴더 상세 정리해보기 (2)","readingTime":{"text":"9 min read"}},"listingPagePath":"/blog"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3262260831","948380417"],"slicesMap":{}}